N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4119.2 - Profanity

State Regulations

No licensee of the commission shall use improper language
or otherwise abuse any official, appointee, representative or employee of the
commission, or any person acting under the orders or rules of the
commission. Notes
